description: Erection of a one-, four- and five-storey block and a two-, four-, five-, eight- and nine-storey block, to provide 145 key-worker residential units comprising 87 key-worker rental flats and 58 shared-ownership units in a mix of 66 one-bedroom, 64 two-bedroom and 15 three-bedroom flats, a meeting room of 40m, with 40 basement car-parking spaces and 33 ground-level car-parking spaces, associated landscaping and bin stores. Provider Report and Application Drawings 09/01/2009) subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 06/05/2009 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended)
